{"tid":836304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【史上首次】韓男團BTS於聯合國發言 籲年輕人勇敢發聲","createTime":"2018-09-25T14:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T04:10:07.000Z","uid":28765,"like":54,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3b609f641ecb7b5b287e398011fbcda3f708a341","tid":836304,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣男團BTS防彈少年團周一到美國紐約聯合國總部，出席聯合國兒童基金會（UNICEF）「無限一代」（Generation Unlimited）活動並發表長達7分鐘的演講，成為首隊在聯合國大會活動上發言的南韓藝人，呼籲年輕人聆聽自己內心的聲音，勇敢說出自己的故事，並希望各國多投資在年輕人身上。<br />\n大會的目標是在2030年前讓所有年輕人得到教育、訓練或職業，出席者包括總統文在寅夫人金正淑、聯合國秘書長古特雷斯及世界銀行行長金墉等。<br />\nBTS的隊長金南俊（RM）用流利的英語分享自己的經歷，指自己在首爾附近出生並度過快樂童年，但大約10歲起開始在意別人的想法而不袒露心聲，最後在音樂找到避風港。即使組成BTS後，聽過別人批評的他也想過放棄，但最後因為隊員和粉絲的支持而堅持至今。<br />\n他又表示，自己雖然會犯錯和有缺點，但仍希望保持原有的樣子，認為大家應該愛自己才可改變生活。金南俊亦表示，發表《Love Yourself: Answer》新碟後，聽到世界各地粉絲的回應，知道團隊幫助他們走過困難並學習自愛，直言：「那些故事時時提醒我們的負任。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180925/large/1537840313_1e0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180925%2Flarge%2F1537840313_1e0d.jpg&h=59798da2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓男團BTS成為首隊於聯合國發言的歌手。<br />\n南韓《韓國先驅報》／韓聯社  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180925/58720521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180925%2F58720521&d=7iDsfgrlGht%2Fgv6gDAikRV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=72837fdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180925%2F58720521&h=3a7cc4c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180925/58720521</a>"},{"pid":"250865bb9fcaa6a977cbca247cf772545f48050f","tid":836304,"uid":113830,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b833c86587ecf5b6f5b27b15396b67abba8db92","tid":836304,"uid":143499,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:32:56.000Z","msg":"好事，不過個look格格不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157fbd3ef31938ae90b84632f5eb7116c3e25c79","tid":836304,"uid":113830,"like":28,"dislike":5,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"6b833c86587ecf5b6f5b27b15396b67abba8db92","tid":836304,"uid":143499,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:32:56.000Z","msg":"好事，不過個look格格不入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"他又表示，自己雖然會犯錯和有缺點，但仍<span style=\"color: red;\">希望保持原有的樣子，認為大家應該愛自己才可改變生活。</span><br />\n<br />\nmind your own business"},{"pid":"f1f5fe2a8c8c72f3697f44180e16a05e5cebe576","tid":836304,"uid":170383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af9e1f60496f1b9c88e8cf79f9e50847c517448","tid":836304,"uid":206853,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"好撚勁"},{"pid":"d0776a0085864eefaffdbc5598ee2996efd90db2","tid":836304,"uid":25535,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T18:08:23.000Z","msg":"聯合國果然係一個笑話"},{"pid":"6c8ca040a8505125f8e3b78843ef8549c4c53bd3","tid":836304,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T18:25:20.000Z","msg":"呢隊野係咪最紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43464f8ea1f53c82a091f9f828eb5527ab5bb6f4","tid":836304,"uid":104443,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T18:47:45.000Z","msg":"真係想睇下佢地「原有的樣子」係咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85593c8a157be4a233